    articleMarkdown: "## 简介\r\nAnother Redis DeskTop Manager 是Redis桌面可视化工具\r\n\r\nAnother Redis DeskTop Manager是基于electron构建。目前可以运行在Windows、Linux、Mac平台。如果想学习electron的，也可以看看这个项目的源码。\r\n## 下载安装\r\n[安装教程](https://github.com/qishibo/AnotherRedisDesktopManager/ \"安装教程\")\r\n[GitHub下载](https://github.com/qishibo/AnotherRedisDesktopManager/releases \"GitHub\")\r\n[码云下载](https://gitee.com/qishibo/AnotherRedisDesktopManager/releases \"码云\")\r\n## 变更日志\r\n2020-06-18: SSL/TLS Support!!!\r\n2020-04-28: Page Zoom && Big Key Loads With Scan && Auto Json\r\n2020-04-18: Unvisible Key\\Value Format Support\r\n2020-04-04: Cluster Support!!!\r\n2020-03-13: Dark Mode Support!!! && JsonView In Other Place\r\n2020-02-16: SSH Private Key Support\r\n2020-02-13: Open Cli Console In Tabs\r\n2019-06-14: Custom Font-Family Support\r\n2019-05-28: Key List Resizable\r\n2019-05-09: Search Support In Hash List Set Zset\r\n2019-04-26: Auto Updater\r\n2019-04-09: SSH Tunnel Connection Support\r\n2019-04-01: Extract Search Support\r\n2019-02-22: Single Connection Support\r\n2019-01-08: Project Start\r\n## 特性\r\n**Another Redis DeskTop Manager支持四种语言**\r\n\r\n![](http://76.nanshengbbs.top/illustration-20200828170013_file_1598605213000.png)\r\n\r\n**首次连redis需要输入用户名和密码等信息**\r\n\r\n![](http://76.nanshengbbs.top/illustration-20200828170121_file_1598605279000.png)\r\n\r\n**进入首页界面（UI效果明显比Redis DeskTop Manager强太多了）**\r\n\r\n![](http://76.nanshengbbs.top/illustration-20200828170248_file_1598605368000.png)\r\n\r\n**查看自己项目存放redis的16个库情况**\r\n\r\n![](http://76.nanshengbbs.top/illustration-20200828170313_file_1598605393000.png)\r\n\r\n**Another Redis DeskTop Manager支持三种文本形式**\r\n\r\n![](http://76.nanshengbbs.top/illustration-20200828170524_file_1598605525000.png)\r\n## 对比\r\nRedis DeskTop Manager也是一款不错的Redis桌面可视化工具，通过对比，**Another Redis DeskTop Manager**在功能和UI上明显高于Redis DeskTop Manager，而且还是开源，果断支持！",
    articleHtml: "<h2><a id=\"_0\"></a>简介</h2>\r\n<p>Another Redis DeskTop Manager 是Redis桌面可视化工具</p>\r\n<p>Another Redis DeskTop Manager是基于electron构建。目前可以运行在Windows、Linux、Mac平台。如果想学习electron的，也可以看看这个项目的源码。</p>\r\n<h2><a id=\"_4\"></a>下载安装</h2>\r\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/qishibo/AnotherRedisDesktopManager/\" title=\"安装教程\" target=\"_blank\">安装教程</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://github.com/qishibo/AnotherRedisDesktopManager/releases\" title=\"GitHub\" target=\"_blank\">GitHub下载</a><br />\r\n<a href=\"https://gitee.com/qishibo/AnotherRedisDesktopManager/releases\" title=\"码云\" target=\"_blank\">码云下载</a></p>\r\n<h2><a id=\"_8\"></a>变更日志</h2>\r\n<p>2020-06-18: SSL/TLS Support!!!<br />\r\n2020-04-28: Page Zoom &amp;&amp; Big Key Loads With Scan &amp;&amp; Auto Json<br />\r\n2020-04-18: Unvisible Key\\Value Format Support<br />\r\n2020-04-04: Cluster Support!!!<br />\r\n2020-03-13: Dark Mode Support!!! &amp;&amp; JsonView In Other Place<br />\r\n2020-02-16: SSH Private Key Support<br />\r\n2020-02-13: Open Cli Console In Tabs<br />\r\n2019-06-14: Custom Font-Family Support<br />\r\n2019-05-28: Key List Resizable<br />\r\n2019-05-09: Search Support In Hash List Set Zset<br />\r\n2019-04-26: Auto Updater<br />\r\n2019-04-09: SSH Tunnel Connection Support<br />\r\n2019-04-01: Extract Search Support<br />\r\n2019-02-22: Single Connection Support<br />\r\n2019-01-08: Project Start</p>\r\n<h2><a id=\"_24\"></a>特性</h2>\r\n<p><strong>Another Redis DeskTop Manager支持四种语言</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://76.nanshengbbs.top/illustration-20200828170013_file_1598605213000.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>首次连redis需要输入用户名和密码等信息</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://76.nanshengbbs.top/illustration-20200828170121_file_1598605279000.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>进入首页界面（UI效果明显比Redis DeskTop Manager强太多了）</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://76.nanshengbbs.top/illustration-20200828170248_file_1598605368000.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>查看自己项目存放redis的16个库情况</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://76.nanshengbbs.top/illustration-20200828170313_file_1598605393000.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p><strong>Another Redis DeskTop Manager支持三种文本形式</strong></p>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://76.nanshengbbs.top/illustration-20200828170524_file_1598605525000.png\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<h2><a id=\"_44\"></a>对比</h2>\r\n<p>Redis DeskTop Manager也是一款不错的Redis桌面可视化工具，通过对比，<strong>Another Redis DeskTop Manager</strong>在功能和UI上明显高于Redis DeskTop Manager，而且还是开源，果断支持！</p>\r\n",
