    articleId: NumberInt("35"),
    articleMarkdown: "#### Disabled options\r\n\r\n- TeX (Based on KaTeX);\r\n- Emoji;\r\n- Task lists;\r\n- HTML tags decode;\r\n- Flowchart and Sequence Diagram;\r\n\r\n#### Editor.md directory\r\n\r\n    editor.md/\r\n            lib/\r\n            css/\r\n            scss/\r\n            tests/\r\n            fonts/\r\n            images/\r\n            plugins/\r\n            examples/\r\n            languages/     \r\n            editormd.js\r\n            ...\r\n\r\n```html\r\n<!-- English -->\r\n<script src=\"../dist/js/languages/en.js\"></script>\r\n\r\n<!-- 繁體中文 -->\r\n<script src=\"../dist/js/languages/zh-tw.js\"></script>\r\n```\r\n#### 图片测试\r\n![](http://76.nanshengbbs.top/illustration-20200604000317_0dc9eb2eff19b29.jpg)\r\n#### 文本测试\r\n##### 1，获取md的内容和html内容\r\n```javascript\r\n//markdown格式的内容\r\n$(\".editormd-markdown-textarea\").attr(\"name\", \"content\");\r\n//markdown的html格式的博文\r\n$(\".editormd-html-textarea\").attr(\"name\", \"html\");\r\n```\r\n##### 2，上传图片问题\r\n```javascript\r\neditormd({\r\n        id: 'articlemd', //编辑(格式化)的ID\r\n        width: '100%',\r\n        height: 640,\r\n        path: markDownConsts.editorMdPath, //路径\r\n        saveHTMLToTextarea: true, //开启保存HTML文件\r\n        htmlDecode: \"iframe,pre\",\r\n        /**上传图片相关配置如下*/\r\n        imageUpload: true,\r\n        imageFormats: [\"jpg\", \"jpeg\", \"gif\", \"png\", \"bmp\", \"webp\"], //图片上传格式\r\n        imageUploadURL: \"path/upload\",\r\n        onload: function () { //上传成功之后的回调\r\n\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n```",
    articleHtml: "<h4><a id=\"Disabled_options_0\"></a>Disabled options</h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li>TeX (Based on KaTeX);</li>\r\n<li>Emoji;</li>\r\n<li>Task lists;</li>\r\n<li>HTML tags decode;</li>\r\n<li>Flowchart and Sequence Diagram;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<h4><a id=\"Editormd_directory_8\"></a>Editor.md directory</h4>\r\n<pre><code>editor.md/\r\n        lib/\r\n        css/\r\n        scss/\r\n        tests/\r\n        fonts/\r\n        images/\r\n        plugins/\r\n        examples/\r\n        languages/     \r\n        editormd.js\r\n        ...\r\n</code></pre>\r\n<pre><div class=\"hljs\"><code class=\"lang-html\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">&lt;!-- English --&gt;</span>\r\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">script</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">src</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;../dist/js/languages/en.js&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">script</span>&gt;</span>\r\n\r\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">&lt;!-- 繁體中文 --&gt;</span>\r\n<span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;<span class=\"hljs-name\">script</span> <span class=\"hljs-attr\">src</span>=<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;../dist/js/languages/zh-tw.js&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class=\"hljs-tag\">&lt;/<span class=\"hljs-name\">script</span>&gt;</span>\r\n</code></div></pre>\r\n<h4><a id=\"_30\"></a>图片测试</h4>\r\n<p><img src=\"http://76.nanshengbbs.top/illustration-20200604000317_0dc9eb2eff19b29.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<h4><a id=\"_32\"></a>文本测试</h4>\r\n<h5><a id=\"1mdhtml_33\"></a>1，获取md的内容和html内容</h5>\r\n<pre><div class=\"hljs\"><code class=\"lang-javascript\"><span class=\"hljs-comment\">//markdown格式的内容</span>\r\n$(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;.editormd-markdown-textarea&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">attr</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;name&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;content&quot;</span>);\r\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">//markdown的html格式的博文</span>\r\n$(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;.editormd-html-textarea&quot;</span>).<span class=\"hljs-title function_\">attr</span>(<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;name&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;html&quot;</span>);\r\n</code></div></pre>\r\n<h5><a id=\"2_40\"></a>2，上传图片问题</h5>\r\n<pre><div class=\"hljs\"><code class=\"lang-javascript\"><span class=\"hljs-title function_\">editormd</span>({\r\n        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">id</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;articlemd&#x27;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//编辑(格式化)的ID</span>\r\n        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">width</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">&#x27;100%&#x27;</span>,\r\n        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">height</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">640</span>,\r\n        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">path</span>: markDownConsts.<span class=\"hljs-property\">editorMdPath</span>, <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//路径</span>\r\n        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">saveHTMLToTextarea</span>: <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>, <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//开启保存HTML文件</span>\r\n        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">htmlDecode</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;iframe,pre&quot;</span>,\r\n        <span class=\"hljs-comment\">/**上传图片相关配置如下*/</span>\r\n        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">imageUpload</span>: <span class=\"hljs-literal\">true</span>,\r\n        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">imageFormats</span>: [<span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;jpg&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;jpeg&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;gif&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;png&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;bmp&quot;</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;webp&quot;</span>], <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//图片上传格式</span>\r\n        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">imageUploadURL</span>: <span class=\"hljs-string\">&quot;path/upload&quot;</span>,\r\n        <span class=\"hljs-attr\">onload</span>: <span class=\"hljs-keyword\">function</span> (<span class=\"hljs-params\"></span>) { <span class=\"hljs-comment\">//上传成功之后的回调</span>\r\n\r\n        }\r\n    });\r\n</code></div></pre>\r\n",
